Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:32.36,signs,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(528,520)\fnFranklin Gothic Medium\pos(641,667)\b1\fscx117\fscy96\c&H000000&\blur3}North Arizona Black Point Lava Flow Training Grounds
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.06,0:10:46.11,Default,A,0,0,0,,Barren earth, craters,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.16,0:10:49.42,Default,A,0,0,0,,treacherous cliffs, steep slopes,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.16,0:10:52.67,Default,A,0,0,0,,extreme temperature swings between day and night,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.51,0:10:57.63,Default,A,0,0,0,,dried-up riverbeds, and clouds of dust with every step.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.36,Default,A,0,0,0,,Well? Are you excited now?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:01.36,0:11:03.80,Default,A,0,0,0,,It's as good as a theme park.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:07.00,0:11:08.27,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Well...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.66,0:11:12.77,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm pretty sure a theme park would be more fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:18.23,0:11:23.91,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I'm one of the weirdos who can get excited about barren desert.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.12,Default,A,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:29.12,0:11:31.62,Default,A,0,0,0,,It's the prime crew of CES-62.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:32.06,0:11:34.88,Default,A,0,0,0,,They started training three days ago.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.14,0:11:44.39,Default,A,0,0,0,,Hey, Vince!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.39,0:11:47.26,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Wow, they all look important...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.63,0:11:51.36,Default,A,0,0,0,,Hey, backup crew members!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:51.36,0:11:53.52,Default,A,0,0,0,,Let's train hard!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:53.92,0:11:55.27,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.57,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Yah, man!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.96,0:12:00.26,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Okay, time to unleash my dreads!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:04.12,0:12:07.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? The prime crew has six members?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:08.26,0:12:10.55,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then we're one short.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.12,0:12:17.13,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that supposed to happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:23.43,0:12:25.35,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,It's so hot...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.14,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,And it's supposed to be December?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.86,0:12:32.11,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must thank the heat!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:33.34,0:12:38.15,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah, this woman is built...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.00,0:12:46.18,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}A heart tattoo... On her left shoulder!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:49.77,0:12:51.87,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like Apo!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Funny thing...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:57.88,0:12:58.50,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.10,0:13:05.51,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,My pet dog also has a heart-shaped mark on his left shoulder.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.86,0:13:07.55,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,Oh? Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.39,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,I think we'll get along great.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.08,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.38,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, that is definitely
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.41,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}not what would happen!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.36,0:13:30.44,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wants to be compared to a dog?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.44,0:13:31.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I almost screwed up.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:39.04,0:13:41.25,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.84,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,Want me to sock you?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.86,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,N-No, s-sorry...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.51,0:13:52.22,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sh-She's strong.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.21,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's really strong!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.21,0:13:55.64,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}And scary.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:56.03,0:13:58.36,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,You're such a fool...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:59.60,0:14:03.15,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,You can't stare at Betty for longer than two seconds.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.40,0:14:10.51,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Why do you think they would assign a beautiful woman like her to a crew full of men?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.83,0:14:16.55,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,It's because she's manlier than the rest of us.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.25,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:21.38,0:14:24.09,Default,A,0,0,0,,Okay, here we are!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.09,0:14:25.99,Default,A,0,0,0,,Thanks for driving safely.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:26.72,0:14:31.24,Default,A,0,0,0,,But it turns out that any idiot can drive this thing safely.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.24,0:14:33.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,This would place last in a Formula 1.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.05,Default,A,0,0,0,,But it rules on the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.49,0:14:39.02,Default,A,0,0,0,,Hello, everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.42,0:14:40.68,Default,A,0,0,0,,I'm Tully.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.68,0:14:42.38,Default,A,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.38,0:14:46.99,Default,A,0,0,0,,So, I'm supposed to teach you how to operate this thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.34,0:14:51.06,Default,A,0,0,0,,But I imagine that some of you already know how it works, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.06,0:14:51.95,Default,A,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:52.37,0:14:56.21,Default,A,0,0,0,,As you know, this is the SEV, also known as the Beetle.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:57.32,0:14:59.72,Default,A,0,0,0,,It cost seven billion dollars to develop!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.72,0:15:03.79,Default,A,0,0,0,,On my salary, I couldn't afford that in a thousand lifetimes.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:04.70,0:15:08.73,Default,A,0,0,0,,Well, if I become a Hollywood star in my next life, I might have a chance...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.93,Default,A,0,0,0,,Yes! I have hope!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:11.26,0:15:13.93,Default,B,0,0,0,,Tully, stop getting sidetracked.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, of course...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:16.38,0:15:17.92,Default,T,0,0,0,,Sorry, George.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:19.64,0:15:22.48,Default,T,0,0,0,,Damn that ape.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:22.48,0:15:24.52,Default,T,0,0,0,,You're the distraction here.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.52,0:15:26.29,Default,T,0,0,0,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.29,0:15:29.61,Default,T,0,0,0,,That's why your wife left you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.16,Default,T,0,0,0,,Not that I have a wife.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.10,0:15:35.87,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,In my next life, I hope to be myself again.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.24,0:15:46.38,Default,T,0,0,0,,The tires can turn 360 degrees, so it can move sideways, like a crab.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.38,0:15:52.08,Default,T,0,0,0,,There are living quarters inside, so it's like a lunar RV.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.08,0:15:53.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Does everyone like to camp?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.78,0:15:54.88,Default,T,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.66,0:15:58.75,Default,T,0,0,0,,You already know that the spacesuits attach to the back, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.19,Default,T,0,0,0,,Right now, they're inside the glove.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.02,0:16:05.05,Default,T,0,0,0,,Oh, the glove is this cover.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.05,0:16:07.13,Default,T,0,0,0,,Reminds you of larva, yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.13,0:16:10.24,Default,T,0,0,0,,Its purpose is to protect spacesuits from regolith.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:10.55,0:16:15.96,Default,T,0,0,0,,It's a convenient tool, but astronauts hate using it...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.96,0:16:22.17,Default,T,0,0,0,,Honestly, do they realize how hard we're working on their behalf?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:22.17,0:16:24.25,Default,T,0,0,0,,Does anyone have any questions?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.76,0:16:26.78,Default,T,0,0,0,,Nope... Of course.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.85,Default,G,0,0,0,,Okay, raise the glove.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.42,0:16:56.98,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.00,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spacesuits for walking on the moon!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:06.04,0:17:08.32,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm about to put one on?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.01,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's finally time!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.88,0:17:14.66,Default,G,0,0,0,,You'll start by learning to put the spacesuit on.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:14.66,0:17:15.88,Default,G,0,0,0,,Who wants to go first?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.26,0:17:17.88,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Then, I'll go first.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:17.88,0:17:19.41,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.41,0:17:21.39,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:21.72,0:17:25.84,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,And that is exactly your problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.84,0:17:26.52,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Betty...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:27.08,0:17:30.24,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,You should have the honor of going first.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.24,0:17:32.44,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,I appreciate it, Carlo.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.95,0:17:38.41,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,But you're still a chauvinist pig.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.78,0:17:40.48,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,qcd,Yeah, oink oink.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.41,0:17:44.72,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,I didn't want you to wear the spacesuit first.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.72,0:17:49.20,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,After all, you probably don't wash those dreads.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.92,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,I wash them! Once every five days!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.92,0:17:55.84,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Five days?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.15,Default,Betty,0,0,0,,{\i1}These guys are so noisy...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.29,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there like a moai...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:01.29,0:18:04.21,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Tell that sleazeball off, man.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.22,0:18:09.15,Default,Andy,0,0,0,,You should wash them every day.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.02,0:18:17.03,Default,G,0,0,0,,You go first.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:17.38,0:18:18.80,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's up with this team?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:26.46,0:18:29.92,Default,Phillip,0,0,0,,Take a sniff... They don't smell!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:29.92,0:18:31.04,Default,Andy,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.04,0:18:31.96,Default,Carlo,0,0,0,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.54,0:18:35.92,Default,G,0,0,0,,Keep it down! There are two more spacesuits!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.89,0:18:41.36,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't see myself going to space with them.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:47.90,0:18:51.56,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\an8}The CES-62 prime crew features a strong lineup...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.29,Default,But,0,0,0,,Angus, Bold, Larry, and Tara.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:55.29,0:18:56.75,Default,But,0,0,0,,They should do just fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:57.73,0:19:01.74,Default,But,0,0,0,,However, the sub crew concerns me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.14,0:19:03.69,Default,A,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.84,0:19:09.12,Default,But,0,0,0,,The sub crew is comprised of some unique characters.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:10.18,0:19:16.62,Default,But,0,0,0,,With his silence and giant size, Andy Tyler can scare people off.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.03,0:19:24.37,Default,But,0,0,0,,Betty Rain's aggressive tone and behavior makes it seem as though she's keeping people away.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.34,0:19:30.73,Default,But,0,0,0,,Carlo Greco is disliked because of his haughty demeanor.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.56,0:19:36.90,Default,But,0,0,0,,Philippe Louis is usually too loud and happy for everyone else.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.67,0:19:40.96,Default,A,0,0,0,,I understand... This could be a problem.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.96,0:19:46.33,Default,But,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, no one wants to go to space with them.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:47.94,0:19:52.65,Default,But,0,0,0,,That's why we ended up putting them together.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.46,Default,But,0,0,0,,We assigned the lonely astronauts to the same team,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:57.97,0:20:01.37,Default,But,0,0,0,,and then we added Nanba Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.05,0:20:08.72,Default,But,0,0,0,,Whether this works or not will be a gamble.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.25,Default,But,0,0,0,,And with one more person,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:14.50,0:20:17.22,Default,But,0,0,0,,the captain of the crew,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:17.22,0:20:19.23,Default,But,0,0,0,,it just might work.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.87,0:20:21.57,Default,A,0,0,0,,Do you know who you'll turn to?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.20,Default,But,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:27.05,0:20:30.12,Default,But,0,0,0,,When I sent an e-mail, I was turned down...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.55,Default,But,0,0,0,,But I have a candidate.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:40.09,0:20:40.09,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:51.86,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,520)}The starlight illuminates my future, it's wow... truth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.57,0:20:58.20,ED,,0,0,0,,It's 3 AM, and I dream awake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:21:01.91,ED,,0,0,0,,With no idea of my future
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:07.21,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,521)}only impatience consumes me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:16.26,ED,,0,0,0,,I have a thorn in my heart that won't allow me to lose to him
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:21.43,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,519)}I'm walking a path of thorns I made for myself
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.72,0:21:27.06,ED,,0,0,0,,But I won't forget the love I found
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:30.77,ED,,0,0,0,,And I won't forget the ones close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.77,0:21:36.61,ED,,0,0,0,,I realized you cannot live your life alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.61,0:21:44.28,ED,,0,0,0,,The starlight illuminates my future, and we are all shooting stars
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:52.33,ED,,0,0,0,,My holy wishes turn all our sad lies into something better
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:56.00,ED,,0,0,0,,Our orbits have gotten separated,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:22:00.80,ED,,0,0,0,,but I'm fine if you are close
