Dialogue: 5,0:22:10.01,0:22:10.01,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.50,0:22:16.39,preview,But,0,0,0,,If he agrees to be captain of Nanba Mutta's team, it just might work.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.39,0:22:19.92,preview,Hibi,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Sharon has come to Houston.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.92,0:22:21.48,preview,Hibi,0,0,0,,Next time, on {\i0}Space Brothers{\i1}:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.79,0:22:23.31,preview,Hibi,0,0,0,,"In the Corner of My Heart"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:25.03,preview,chapter,0,0,0,,{Mr. Hibbit}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:31.90,0:22:33.82,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,Mr. Hibbit!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:36.09,0:22:37.75,Default,Fred,0,0,0,,What's going on? {D: It's kind of weird, but I think this is an earlier omake episode. Not sure if that's intentional or what...}
Dialogue: 5,0:22:38.53,0:22:40.79,Default,N,0,0,0,,Fire detected in Module 5.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:40.79,0:22:42.56,Default,N,0,0,0,,Fire-suppression system is malfunctioning.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.17,Default,N,0,0,0,,Possibility of explosion.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:45.70,0:22:48.11,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Don't we need to get out of here?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:48.11,0:22:52.14,Default,Linda,0,0,0,,But we can't leave until Beetle finishes charging.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:52.51,0:22:54.39,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,So we have nowhere to run?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:54.39,0:22:56.26,Default,Karen,0,0,0,,Isn't there anything we can do?
Dialogue: 5,0:22:56.26,0:22:57.60,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Let's find a way!
Dialogue: 5,0:22:59.58,0:23:02.89,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Everyone, it's time to combine our powers!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:02.89,0:23:04.48,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Use whatever you've got.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:04.97,0:23:07.57,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Freddy Dog can provide experience and leadership.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:08.43,0:23:10.03,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Damian Hawk provides technical expertise.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.53,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Buddy Gorilla provides brawn.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:13.14,0:23:16.49,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Red Panda Linda and Karen Cat provide knowledge and support.
Dialogue: 5,0:23:17.17,0:23:19.64,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,It's time to unite...
Dialogue: 5,0:23:19.64,0:23:20.83,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I'll let you guys handle this!
Dialogue: 5,0:23:20.83,0:23:22.82,Default,Bud,0,0,0,,Wait up, Hibbit...
